            <summary>Manuscript is a series of various instructional texts to be consulted by a Jain monk or other figure installing images for use in Jaina rites of image worship (pūjā). Has an image towards the end of the roll depicting a multi-leveled maṇḍala (circle) with numerous mantras dedicated to Jaina deities.</summary>
